# zcfan profile: ThinkPad L14 Gen 4 (AMD Ryzen 5, integrated Radeon)
# Thin ultraportable with a small fan and a cool-running 15-28W APU: keep the
# fan off at idle and ramp later/softer for quieter operation. Zen 3 mobile is
# happy into the high 80s, so there is plenty of thermal headroom.
max_temp 90
med_temp 75
low_temp 60
temp_hysteresis 10

max_level full-speed
med_level 3
low_level 0
